<para><computeroutput>int take_grid (int three, int five, int seven)</computeroutput></para><para>

<para>for taking a valid grid value and prompting the user to give a valid grid value. </para>
</para>

<para>if 0 is returned the prompt ask for the grid value again. if -1 is returned terminate the game. only valid inputs are 3, 5 and 7. if the chosen grid has no available circles, that particular grid is no longer a valid input.</para>

